      "lang": "en",
      "text": "6 Precious Metals Quarterly 2012 Q3 Executive Summary CRU International Limited confidential Data sources and study team The historical data presented in this report are based on estimates published by a variety of sources, including Johnson Matthey (JM), World Gold Council (WGC), International Financial Statistics (IFS), JD Power, London Bullion Market Association (LBMA), World Bureau of Metal Statistics (WBMS), GTIS trade statistics, and company websites and written reports. However, CRU’s interpretation of these data may or may not coincide with those expressed in these various sources. The forecast is exclusively CRU’s. This report is based on information available to CRU up until 14th September 2012. CRU Lead, Zinc and Precious Metals Team Graham Deller (Manager) * Neil Hawkes Kirill Kirilenko * Giles Lloyd * Helen O’Cleary Ashok Patel * Contributors to the current issue of the Precious Metals Quarterly Comments or queries will be welcomed by any of the contributors, but particularly:- Kirill Kirilenko –  +44 (0)20 7903 2282 and e-mail kirill.kirilenko@crugroup.com Giles Lloyd –  +44 (0)20 7903 2094 and e-mail giles.lloyd@crugroup.com Graham Deller –  +44 (0)20 7903 2097",
